<subSubSection id="C3556504FF9AFFECF3C2FD742DC27732" pageId="121" pageNumber="122" type="description">
<paragraph id="8BF0368FFF9AFFECF3C2FD742DC27732" blockId="121.[151,1436,649,1465]" pageId="121" pageNumber="122">
<emphasis id="B93BEA9DFF9AFFECF3C2FD742F20769D" bold="true" box="[151,296,649,674]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="121" pageNumber="122" reason="1">Description.</emphasis>
Kirkaldy describes the species as follows (original description in French): Bright blood-red; legs yellowish brown, tinted with red; forewings hyaline, very faintly infuscated here and there, veins colourless, except for a subapical line and the adjacent sections of the longitudinal veins, which are blood red. Length to tip of abdomen 2 1/ 
<quantity id="4CB79B6AFF9AFFECF3ADFD082F357732" box="[248,317,757,781]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="8.0" pageId="121" pageNumber="122" unit="mm" value="8.0">8 mm</quantity>
; expanded forewings 
<quantity id="4CB79B6AFF9AFFECF164FD082C7D7732" box="[561,629,757,781]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="121" pageNumber="122" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
. Habitat: 
<collectingRegion id="498BF86DFF9AFFECF1B4FD0B2D1B7732" box="[737,787,758,781]" country="Indonesia" name="Jawa Timur" pageId="121" pageNumber="122">Java</collectingRegion>
(van Deventer).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C3556504FF9AFFECF392FCE42A74770E" box="[199,1148,793,817]" pageId="121" pageNumber="122" type="etymology">
