<emphasis id="B93BEA9DFF9AFFECF052FCE72DEB770E" box="[775,995,794,817]" italics="true" pageId="121" pageNumber="122">sanguineus, -a, -um</emphasis>
= blood red).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
